stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft: Create
    Draft --> Active: Start Session
    Active --> Paused: Pause
    Paused --> Active: Resume
    Active --> Ended: End Session
    Ended --> [*]
    
    note right of Draft
        Session in draft mode
        Admin/moderator can:
        - Create polls
        - Upload media
        - Configure settings
    end note
    
    note right of Active
        Session is live
        Participants can:
        - Join session
        - Vote on polls
        - Increment counter
        - View materials
    end note
    
    note right of Paused
        Session temporarily paused
        No new votes accepted
        Existing data preserved
    end note
    
    note right of Ended
        Session completed
        Read-only access
        Results available
    end note
